DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Tell me more about these dragons.
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Tell me more about these dragons.

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about the Dragonkin?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about the Dragonkin?

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about the Garou?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about the Garou?

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Queen Kuldra?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Queen Kuldra?

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about the previous adventurer?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about the previous adventurer?

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Velgar?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Velgar?

Message.SourceString: Relatively little is known about the Dragonkin, less still the ones who set up shop here.
Message.LocalizedString: Relatively little is known about the Dragonkin, less still the ones who set up shop here.

Message.SourceString: We know that they're ancient, dangerous and constantly angry. They were cursed by the elder gods a long, long, long time ago.
Message.LocalizedString: We know that they're ancient, dangerous and constantly angry. They were cursed by the elder gods a long, long, long time ago.

Message.SourceString: They have a penchant for two things that interest us. First, they make dragons, which is the problem we're facing right now.
Message.LocalizedString: They have a penchant for two things that interest us. First, they make dragons, which is the problem we're facing right now.

Message.SourceString: Secondly, they hoard secrets like they're more valuable than gold... or party hats.
Message.LocalizedString: Secondly, they hoard secrets like they're more valuable than gold... or party hats.

Message.SourceString: When my comrades and I set foot on Ashenfall, we thought it would be paradise. Lush green fields, tall and resilient trees  a world unsullied.
Message.LocalizedString: When my comrades and I set foot on Ashenfall, we thought it would be paradise. Lush green fields, tall and resilient trees  a world unsullied.

Message.SourceString: But then dragons happened.
Message.LocalizedString: But then dragons happened.

Message.SourceString: They swooped down from the skies and decimated the landing party. Whole teams of people, gone, just like that.
Message.LocalizedString: They swooped down from the skies and decimated the landing party. Whole teams of people, gone, just like that.

Message.SourceString: "Queen Kuldra bids you welcome," they laughed, as our comrades drew their final breaths.
Message.LocalizedString: "Queen Kuldra bids you welcome," they laughed, as our comrades drew their final breaths.

Message.SourceString: So here's the deal: I need you to kill them all. Show these dragons and their Queen, that we're not just going to roll over and die.
Message.LocalizedString: So here's the deal: I need you to kill them all. Show these dragons and their Queen, that we're not just going to roll over and die.

Message.SourceString: We fight back, and we fight back hard.
Message.LocalizedString: We fight back, and we fight back hard.

Message.SourceString: Their vaults will be guarded, but well worth exploring. You never know what you might find in there.
Message.LocalizedString: Their vaults will be guarded, but well worth exploring. You never know what you might find in there.

Message.SourceString: General Velgar, let that sink in. A title, on a dragon, not a good sign.
Message.LocalizedString: General Velgar, let that sink in. A title, on a dragon, not a good sign.

Message.SourceString: I don't have much for you there, Vannaka's the one investigating them. He's pushing his way into Ghornfell, you should look for him there.
Message.LocalizedString: I don't have much for you there, Vannaka's the one investigating them. He's pushing his way into Ghornfell, you should look for him there.

Message.SourceString: What I know is that the garou are merciless. They'll cut you down without a chance to speak.
Message.LocalizedString: What I know is that the garou are merciless. They'll cut you down without a chance to speak.

Message.SourceString: We don't know much at the moment, since everyone who's seen him is dead.
Message.LocalizedString: We don't know much at the moment, since everyone who's seen him is dead.

Message.SourceString: But he's big, scary and he wants to make all of us wyrm food. So, diplomacy's out.
Message.LocalizedString: But he's big, scary and he wants to make all of us wyrm food. So, diplomacy's out.

Message.SourceString: I know very little about this Kuldra character, except that Velgar pledged his loyalty to her.
Message.LocalizedString: I know very little about this Kuldra character, except that Velgar pledged his loyalty to her.

Message.SourceString: From what I can gather, she's something like royalty to the dragons here; never a good sign.
Message.LocalizedString: From what I can gather, she's something like royalty to the dragons here; never a good sign.

Message.SourceString: She's spoken of not with the reverence due a monarch, but with the devotion due a deity.
Message.LocalizedString: She's spoken of not with the reverence due a monarch, but with the devotion due a deity.

Message.SourceString: I don't like that. Not one itty little bit.
Message.LocalizedString: I don't like that. Not one itty little bit.

Message.SourceString: Cathan, now there was a pain in the neck.
Message.LocalizedString: Cathan, now there was a pain in the neck.

Message.SourceString: Young noble sprog, low down the pecking order. Fifth son, I think. Wanted to be a hero, you know how it goes.
Message.LocalizedString: Young noble sprog, low down the pecking order. Fifth son, I think. Wanted to be a hero, you know how it goes.

Message.SourceString: Beastmen from another world, living only for the hunt. Best avoided if you can, but be prepared for a tough fight where you can't.
Message.LocalizedString: Beastmen from another world, living only for the hunt. Best avoided if you can, but be prepared for a tough fight where you can't.

Message.SourceString: Got into scraps as a boy. Lost his leg to a wolf. Say what you want, he had guts that kid.
Message.LocalizedString: Got into scraps as a boy. Lost his leg to a wolf. Say what you want, he had guts that kid.

Message.SourceString: The "legendary" swordsman Vannaka taught him the art of swordplay, while I instructed him in the arcane.
Message.LocalizedString: The "legendary" swordsman Vannaka taught him the art of swordplay, while I instructed him in the arcane.

Message.SourceString: He was a constant annoyanceloud, irritating, overflowing with relentless optimism. You know the type. Even so, his absence leaves a void.
Message.LocalizedString: He was a constant annoyanceloud, irritating, overflowing with relentless optimism. You know the type. Even so, his absence leaves a void.

Message.SourceString: Anything else I can help you with?
Message.LocalizedString: Anything else I can help you with?
